      • onDelivery

        public void onDelivery(org.apache.qpid.proton.engine.Event event)
        onDelviery is triggered when the AMQP socket receives a message. When the message is received it will create a OKSE message and pass it into the MessageService. It will also add AMQP messages back into the internal AMQP queue to generate less overhead.
        Specified by:
